Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,274)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:00:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hurry up in there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,4297份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,4,297 Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.26,0:01:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Orders up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要撑住  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.82,0:01:37.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:37.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我蟹黄堡怎么还没上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.99,0:01:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.49,0:01:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么拖那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐怎么还没上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are my orders?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也翻不了肉饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't flip patties anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好给我解释清楚  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better explain yourself, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的锅铲断了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My spatula is broken, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了铲铲  我做不了蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't make Krabby Patties without Spatty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲柜那边再拿一把不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just grab another one from the spatula closet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,柜子里的我用不了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't cook with those, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得用我自己的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to use my own spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便找的锅铲不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not just any spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲十分特别  还十分古老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatty is very special and very ancient
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.28,0:02:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在天涯海角的群山之间锻造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was forged deep in the mountains beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,位在遥远无际的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the far-flung land of--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在每秒都会多亏钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm losing money by the second here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要怎么解决  我都不稀罕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好给我速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you better get back in a jiffy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就把你工作全让给海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll just have to give your job to SpongeTom here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我预备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事情不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, anything but that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会把我锅铲重新锻造好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get my spatula reforged
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.14,0:02:44.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:44.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,替我先顶一下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold down the fort for me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我这么多年来用法都不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been using them wrong all these years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:20.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,640)}神秘雾山\N攀爬风险自负
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘雾山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Mystical Misty Mountains
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再往山顶走一小段路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for a short walk to the top
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我这背包可没白背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I didn't carry this backpack for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right on time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来担任你的导游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be your guide today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:53.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,382)}鲁布导游旅行团
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.75,0:03:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先要走过这座神奇的鱼造桥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First up, we will cross this amazing fish-made bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一纸老虎罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is way easier than it looks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在左边的是无穷瘀伤地缝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your left is the chasm of infinite bruising
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太壮观了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在右边的是冻鱼坑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And on your right, we got the freezing pit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟你说很轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you it'd be a breeze
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的表现太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's keep moving
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:46.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,352)}危险 禁止入内
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这咱就各走各的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where we part company
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.14,0:04:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过了这个地方  就只有死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beyond this point lies only death
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我六点下班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plus, I clock out at 6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.98,0:04:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:06.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,446)}危险 禁止入内
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Danger, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西都阻止不了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing will stop us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做出美味的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from flipping delicious Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All better now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了你的神圣打呼仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb your sacred snoring ritual
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我千里迢迢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I have traveled a long way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从蟹堡王厨房赶过来  只想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the kitchen of the Krusty Krab just to get--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say no more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隔油池大师知道海绵宝宝来这的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guru Greasetrap already knows why SpongeBob is here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要的东西这边都有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have just what you need
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蔬果挖球器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,melon ballers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意大利面勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spaghetti spoons
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煮蛋计时器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,egg timers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.05,0:06:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且这个巨型香蕉挂可以特价卖给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there's also a special on this giant banana hanger
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all really nice
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我只想修好我心爱的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I just need to get my beloved spatula fixed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以重新锻造好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you reforge it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你快说可以救回铲铲  隔油池先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please tell me we can save her, Mr. Greasetrap
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这点要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两三分钟就能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll just take a few minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去取一下铁锤和铁砧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let the old man grab his ol' hammer and anvil
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get it for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.29,0:06:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you out of there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}之后
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隔油池要想帮你重新锻造锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greasetrap cannot reforge your spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能等人家双手先痊愈才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until my hands have healed up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.76,0:06:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你的真命之铲就蕴藏在你的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But your true spatula is inside you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.11,0:07:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以教你重新锻造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can teach you to reforge it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  大师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.24,0:07:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  你劈的每一掌都是神圣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, every cut is sacred
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要带着木头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do not carry the wood
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让木头带领你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let the wood carry you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与火焰融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Become one with the fire
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm one with the fire
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大师  时候到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master, is it time yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}很多很多难受的瞬间之后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他绝对没法准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll never be ready
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.70,0:08:03.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:03.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功说服我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You convinced me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隔油池也认为你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greasetrap also thinks you're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吗  铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here that, Spatty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时候总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is finally time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总算回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're finally back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打裤子底感谢你  大师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you from the bottom of my pants, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须找到回蟹堡王的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to find a way back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁还没太迟赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before it's too late
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,406)}迟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,270)}太迟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,736)}早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,834)}准时
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隔油池大师知道有条近道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guru Greasetrap knows a shortcut
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love surprises
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578,712)}神秘雾山停车场
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1618,756)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,406)}迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,270)}太迟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,736)}早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,834)}准时
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time's up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作归你了  海绵汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The job's yours, SpongeTom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的梦想终于实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My dreams are finally coming true
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会回来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be back, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且锅铲也修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm not alone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说  海绵宝宝回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's back, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发光发热时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's our time to shine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.13,0:10:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  你的真命之铲蕴藏在你的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, your true spatula is inside you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与肉饼融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Become one with the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你劈的每一掌都是神圣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every cut is sacred
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让蟹黄堡带领你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the patties carry you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  真是太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, that was amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡  再加一份大份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty and a large--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的手怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hands?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的教诲我铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remembered what you told me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向内心深处探寻我的真命之铲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I went deep within to find my true spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之前说真命之铲蕴藏在内心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I said your true spatula was inside you
