Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come outside
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个惊喜要送你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a surprise for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会爱上的  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna love this, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱死你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,really love it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.95,0:12:13.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是专门给你准备的小窝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a playhouse just for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你跟我一样是一家之主了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're a homeowner just like me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过不用还房贷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,minus the mortgage payments
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go right in
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你爱不爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you love it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的小小窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a playhouse under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在要走了  让你放开了玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna leave you alone to play
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  该进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, time to come in
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gare-bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, buddy
