Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's late
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go inside
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想在你的新小窝里过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wanna spend the night in your new playhouse?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is so cu--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪来的门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd he get a door?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.40,0:13:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你喜欢我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy you like my gift
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, good night
