Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not me
