Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那头死龙虾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That lousy lobster
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry, you meat head
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我放下你手头上做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're doing, stop it
