Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会名垂最可爱之史的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the history of cutest days ever
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too cute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太太太太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too, too, too, too cute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too, too, cute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Precious
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家孩子在骚扰我家孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your kids are harassing my kid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人家只是在玩游戏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're just playing a game
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我们就快赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and we're winning
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a game?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.05,0:17:21.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:21.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是在支持我们自己的队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just rooting for our team
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们队加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay, team us
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你队垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo, team you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是别喝汽水比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should lay off the sodas
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天摄入的糖分已经够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've had enough sugar for today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.97,0:17:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请来一份甜饼冰淇淋甜筒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One sugar cookie ice cream on a sugar cone, please
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加彩糖粒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with extra sugar sprinkles
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}可可爱爱的好多小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个能不能闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you two please shut up?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock it off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个昨天哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where were you two yesterday?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我得亲自管店  亲自收银
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had to manage, run the register
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.87,0:19:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要整天亲自做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and cook all day all by meself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here ya go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就没收过热钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you ever had to handle hot change?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该是整天沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we got carried away
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我们的动物跟身了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,watching our animal double-gaggers all day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫分身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's doppelgangers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.74,0:19:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  那个应该念喷身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I believe it's pronounced bubble hangers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个呆头在唠叨什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you barnacle brains blabbering about?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in Neptune's creation is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么会这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why is it so adorable?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我挪开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scooch over
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  小蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Krabsy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小小蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A tiny little Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.97,0:20:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too cute
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱的观光团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An adorable tour group
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.15,0:20:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen this one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I lived this one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小子就在此时此地度过难关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was where me boy-o really came through
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的辉煌时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My shining moment
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,印象里没这段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember this part
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这里只容得下一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess there's only room for one me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴你又回家住了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to have you back inside, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也很高兴你们两个也能来一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's nice to have you two here as well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too cute
